init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: With the exception of the first and last chapters, every chapter is told by a different character in the form of letters sent to their "future"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The story begins in a small town in the north of France.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Your parents are always busy with their jobs.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It takes place in the same town.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You come across a strange building, and are drawn to it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He seems very ill, and you realize that it is a hospital.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The story may be a dream, but it is the "truth" of the characters.
